#: app/templates/about.html:10
msgid "About Grylli"
msgstr "Mu dheidhinn Grylli"

#: app/templates/about.html:13
msgid ""
"Grylli is a secure, self-hosted message delivery platform that automatically"
" sends pre-configured messages if a user fails to check in within a defined "
"time period."
msgstr ""
"Is e àrd-ùrlar lìbhrigeadh teachdaireachdan tèarainte, fèin-aoigheachd a th’"
" ann an Grylli a chuireas teachdaireachdan rèiteachaidh ro-làimh gu fèin-"
"ghluasadach mura faigh neach-cleachdaidh stiùir taobh a-staigh ùine air a "
"mhìneachadh."

#: app/templates/about.html:14
msgid ""
"It supports multiple users, customizable schedules, and recurring reminders."
msgstr ""
"Tha e a’ toirt taic do grunn luchd-cleachdaidh agus clàran-ama gnàthaichte."

#: app/templates/about.html:15
msgid ""
"Messages and reminders can be delivered via email, webhooks, or over 100 "
"third-party services through Apprise."
msgstr ""
"Faodar teachdaireachdan a lìbhrigeadh tro phost-d, webhooks, no còrr air 80 "
"seirbheis treas-phàrtaidh tro Apprise."

#: app/templates/about.html:16
msgid ""
"Users can configure their own SMTP servers to ensure emails and reminders "
"appear to come directly from them — not from the system administrator."
msgstr ""
"Faodaidh luchd-cleachdaidh na frithealaichean SMTP aca fhèin a rèiteachadh "
"gus dèanamh cinnteach gu bheil teachdaireachdan coltach gu bheil iad a’ "
"tighinn gu dìreach bhuapa — chan e bhon rianadair siostaim."

#: app/templates/about.html:17
msgid ""
"Sensitive data is encrypted at rest, and all operations are secured with "
"strong authentication and audit-friendly logging."
msgstr ""
"Tha dàta mothachail air a chrioptachadh aig fois, agus tha a h-uile obair "
"teachdaireachd tèarainte le dearbhadh làidir agus logadh càirdeil do "
"sgrùdadh."

#: app/templates/about.html:18
msgid ""
"Built with a modern, reactive technology stack, Grylli is optimized for "
"responsiveness and works seamlessly across desktop and mobile devices."
msgstr ""
"Togte le cnap-teicneòlais ùr-nodha, freagairteach, tha Grylli freagarra "
"airson freagairteachd agus ag obair gun bhriseadh thar innealan deasg agus "
"gluasadach."

#: app/templates/about.html:23
msgid "Version:"
msgstr "Tionndadh:"

#: app/templates/about.html:26
msgid "Repository:"
msgstr "Tasg-lann:"

#: app/templates/about.html:30
msgid "GitHub - samcro1967/grylli"
msgstr "GitHub - samcro1967/grylli"

