msgid "Emails"
msgstr "Post-d"

#: app/templates/help.html:34
msgid "View and manage secure email messages"
msgstr "Sealladh farsaing air teachdaireachdan post-d tèarainte"

#: app/templates/help.html:38
msgid "Security"
msgstr "🔐 Tèarainteachd"

#: app/templates/help.html:39
msgid "Grylli encrypts sensitive data and logs all key actions for auditing."
msgstr ""
"Bidh Grylli a’ crioptachadh dàta mothachail agus a’ logadh a h-uile prìomh "
"ghnìomhachd airson sgrùdadh."

#: app/templates/index.html:9 app/views/locale.py:95
msgid "Welcome to Grylli"
msgstr "Fàilte gu Grylli"

#: app/templates/index.html:11
msgid "Pronounced"
msgstr "Air a ràdh"

#: app/templates/index.html:11
msgid "like “grill-ee”"
msgstr "mar “grill-ee”"

#: app/templates/index.html:14
msgid ""
"Grylli is a secure message scheduling and delivery system designed to ensure"
" your important messages are delivered — even if you can’t be there to send "
"them."
msgstr ""
"Tha Grylli na shiostam clàraidh agus lìbhrigeadh teachdaireachd tèarainte a "
"chaidh a dhealbhadh gus dèanamh cinnteach gum bi na teachdaireachdan "
"cudromach agad air an lìbhrigeadh — eadhon mura h-urrainn dhut a bhith ann "
"airson an cur."

#: app/templates/index.html:17
msgid ""
"Whether you’re planning ahead, setting up emergency communication, or "
"building peace of mind, Grylli helps automate your message delivery via "
"multiple channels including email, webhooks, and Apprise notifications."
msgstr ""
"Ge bith a bheil thu a' dealbhadh ro-làimh, a' stèidheachadh conaltradh "
"èiginn, no a' togail fois inntinn, bidh Grylli gad chuideachadh le bhith "
"fèin-ghluasadach ann an lìbhrigeadh teachdaireachd tro phost-d, webhooks, no"
" fiosan Apprise mura caill thu sgrùdadh a-steach."

#: app/templates/index.html:19
msgid "Getting Started"
msgstr "A' Tòiseachadh"

#: app/templates/index.html:21
msgid "Create a message, email, or reminder."
msgstr "Cruthaich teachdaireachd no post-d."

#: app/templates/index.html:22
msgid "Set your check-in interval and grace period (for messages)."
msgstr "Stèidhich an eadar-ama sgrùdaidh agus ùine gràidh."

#: app/templates/index.html:23
msgid "Assign one or more delivery destinations."
msgstr "Sònraich aon no barrachd cheann-uidhe lìbhrigidh."

#: app/templates/index.html:24
msgid "Optionally attach files for secure emails."
msgstr "Roghainneil, ceangail faidhlichean airson puist-d tèarainte."

#: app/templates/index.html:25
msgid "Schedule reminders to send at specific times or on a recurring basis."
msgstr ""
"Clàraich cuimhneachain airson an cur aig amannan sònraichte no air bunait "
"ath-aithris."

#: app/templates/index.html:26
msgid "Enable the message or reminder to activate delivery."
msgstr ""
"Cuir an gnìomh am fios no an cuimhneachan gus lìbhrigeadh a chuir an gnìomh."

#: app/templates/index.html:28
msgid ""
"Regularly check in to Grylli to prevent automated delivery; miss a check-in "
"and Grylli sends your messages as scheduled."
msgstr ""
"Thoir sùil gu cunbhalach air Grylli gus lìbhrigeadh fèin-ghnìomhach a "
"sheachnadh; ma chailleas tu sgrùdadh a-steach, cuiridh Grylli na "
"teachdaireachdan agad mar a chaidh a chlàradh."

#: app/templates/privacy.html:10
msgid "Privacy Notice"
msgstr "Brath Prìobhaideachd"

#: app/templates/privacy.html:13
msgid ""
"Grylli respects your privacy and is designed to minimize the collection and "
"storage of personal data."
msgstr ""
"Tha Grylli a’ toirt urram don phrìobhaideachd agad agus air a dhealbhadh gus"
" lughdachadh a dhèanamh air cruinneachadh agus stòradh dàta pearsanta."

#: app/templates/privacy.html:14
msgid ""
"All data is encrypted where appropriate and remains fully under your control"
" if you self-host this platform."
msgstr ""
"Tha a h-uile dàta air a chrioptaigeadh far a bheil sin iomchaidh agus tha e "
"gu tur fo do smachd ma tha an àrd-ùrlar seo agad air fhèin-aoigheachd."

#: app/templates/privacy.html:17
msgid "What Data We Collect"
msgstr "Dè an Dàta a chruinnicheas sinn"

#: app/templates/privacy.html:19
msgid "Email address and password hash (for authentication)"
msgstr ""
"Seòladh puist-d agus cruth crioptaichte facal-faire (airson dearbhadh)"

#: app/templates/privacy.html:20
msgid "Optional MFA secret and recovery codes (encrypted at rest)"
msgstr ""
"Rùnaire MFA roghainneil agus còdan ath-bheothachaidh (air an crioptaigeadh "
"aig fois)"

#: app/templates/privacy.html:21
msgid "Reminder and message content you configure"
msgstr "Susbaint cuimhneachaidh agus teachdaireachd a chumas tu air dòigh"

#: app/templates/privacy.html:22
msgid "User-specific settings, SMTP configuration (if provided)"
msgstr ""
"Roghainnean aghaidh-lìn sònraichte do neach-cleachdaidh, rèiteachadh SMTP "
"(ma chaidh a thoirt seachad)"

#: app/templates/privacy.html:25
msgid "How Your Data Is Used"
msgstr "Mar a thathas a' cleachdadh an dàta agad"

#: app/templates/privacy.html:27
msgid ""
"Your data is used solely for the purpose of delivering reminders and "
"messages according to your preferences."
msgstr ""
"Tha an dàta agad air a chleachdadh dìreach airson lìbhrigeadh chuimhneachain"
" is theachdaireachdan a rèir do roghainnean."

#: app/templates/privacy.html:28
msgid ""
"Grylli does not share, sell, or transmit your personal data to any third "
"parties."
msgstr ""
"Chan eil Grylli a’ roinn, a’ reic, no a’ cur an dàta pearsanta agad gu treas"
" phàrtaidhean sam bith."

#: app/templates/privacy.html:31
msgid "Your Rights"
msgstr "Na Còraichean agad"

#: app/templates/privacy.html:33
msgid ""
"You can export all of your data at any time from the Account Settings page."
msgstr ""
"Faodaidh tu d’ uile dàta às-mhalairt uair sam bith bhon duilleag Roghainnean"
" Cunntais."

#: app/templates/privacy.html:34
msgid "You may permanently delete your account and all associated data."
msgstr ""
"Chan urrainn dhut do chunntas a sguabadh às oir is tusa am fear rianachd mu "
"dheireadh."

#: app/templates/privacy.html:35
msgid ""
"If you are using a self-hosted instance, contact the instance administrator "
"for data inquiries."
msgstr ""
"Ma tha thu a’ cleachdadh foillseachadh fhèin, cuir fios chun neach-rianachd "
"foillseachaidh airson ceistean dàta."

#: app/templates/privacy.html:38
msgid "Self-Hosting Responsibility"
msgstr "Uallach Fèin-aoigheachd"

#: app/templates/privacy.html:40
msgid ""
"If you are running Grylli on your own server, you are responsible for the "
"storage, processing, and lawful handling of all user data on that instance."
msgstr ""
"Ma tha Grylli agad air an fhrithealaiche agad fhèin, tha thu an urra ri "
"stòradh, giollachd, agus làimhseachadh laghail uile dàta neach-cleachdaidh "
"air an fhoillseachadh sin."

#: app/templates/privacy.html:44
msgid ""
"This notice was last updated in June 2025 and may evolve to reflect changes "
"in the software or regulatory landscape."
msgstr ""
"Chaidh an rabhadh seo ùrachadh mu dheireadh san Ògmhios 2025 agus dh’ "
"fhaodadh e a thighinn air adhart airson atharrachaidhean ann am bathar-bog "
"no ann an sealladh riaghlaidh."

